It’s been almost a week since I lost my Grandfather, Francis❤️Growing up I always wanted to be with my Poppy and Grandy. Eat chocolate ice cream whenever I wanted, take naps with Grandy(often),play on Poppy’s golf cart, the list goes on. He was so sweet but knew how to boss ya around. Could walk fast and fry up some mean catfish. He loved my grandmother and his family unconditionally ❤️ He lived a beautiful life. 
Rest Easy Poppy
